ZH: 我们公司负责代理这个品牌的销售。
EN: Our company is responsible for acting as an agent for the sales of this brand.

ZH: 她在法庭上代理了他的案件。
EN: She acted as his attorney in court.

ZH: 我们可以通过代理购买这个产品。
EN: We can purchase this product through an agent.

ZH: 他是我在这里的代理人。
EN: He is my representative here.

ZH: 代理商在全球范围内销售我们的产品。
EN: The agents sell our products globally.

ZH: 请联系我们的代理部门以获取更多信息。
EN: Please contact our agency department for more information.

ZH: 这家公司是我代理的最新客户。
EN: This company is the latest client I represent.

ZH: 他们通过代理商来进口商品。
EN: They import goods through agents.

ZH: 我们的代理合同即将到期。
EN: Our agency contract is about to expire.

ZH: 请委托律师代理你的离婚案件。
EN: Please appoint a lawyer to handle your divorce case.

ZH: 他成为了该地区公司的代理销售人员。
EN: He became the company's sales representative in that region.

ZH: 代理人在交涉中坚持了客户的利益。
EN: The agent insisted on the interests of the client during the negotiation.

ZH: 我的代理人正在和对方协商合作事宜。
EN: My representative is currently negotiating cooperation matters with the other party.

ZH: 我们需要一个代理商来推广我们的产品。
EN: We need an agent to promote our products.

ZH: 代理商协助我们进行市场调研。
EN: The agent assists us in conducting market research.

ZH: 他们通过代理向用户提供技术支持。
EN: They provide technical support to customers through an agent.

ZH: 你可以通过代理买到这本书。
EN: You can buy this book through a proxy.

ZH: 请找一个可靠的代理人来处理此事。
EN: Please find a reliable proxy to handle this matter.

ZH: 他们通过代理销售该品牌的电视。
EN: They sell televisions from this brand through agents.

ZH: 我的代理商正在与供应商协商价格。
EN: My agent is negotiating prices with suppliers.

ZH: 感谢你替我代理这个重要的会议。
EN: Thank you for representing me in this important meeting.
